flavor_text_entries.ja: 相手の　壁や　身代わりを すりぬけて　攻撃　できる

flavor_text_entries.en: Passes through the opposing Pokémon’s barrier, substitute, and the like and strikes.
flavor_text_entries.fr: Traverse les barrières et les clones de l’ennemi pour attaquer directement.

flavor_text_entries.es: Ataca rodeando la barrera o el sustituto del rival.
